spec_data.Name: python3-flask-restful
spec_data.Description:
Flask-RESTful is Python 3 extension for Flask that adds support
for quickly building REST APIs. It is a lightweight abstraction
that works with your existing ORM/libraries.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 01:03:43 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Simple framework for creating REST APIs for Flask
